				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Plane of Fear<a name="51301"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jul 12 04 2:29 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Depends on how suicidal you are.
<br />

<br />
FWIW, mobs up there have ~10K HP and are level 48-52.  It takes me 3-3.5 minutes to kite down a mob with (3) 134 dots, (1) 105 dot and (1) 57 dot ticking.
<br />

<br />
Can it be done without Fade?  Sure.  You won't have much of a chance for a breather though unless you run out of chase range and camp.
<br />

<br />
I'd have to think in your 50s though, getting rooted or whatever else is much more likely than at 65, and that would be very bad, since it may be very unlikely that you can get a rez.
<br />

<br />
I found charm kiting to be pretty poor.  Mobs break way to often.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
